value.summary:
I am a frontend developer based on the Philippines that helps companies offer long term solutions,  attract visitors and help them signup as well as increase site retention via faster load speed without compromising client-approved design. Well-versed in doing frontend related work even in a high-pressured environment, always looking for ways to improve my craft in every time my code editor is open. 

As a Frontend developer for a long time with over 7 years of professional experience optimizing page speed, creating efficient reusable code building either on React or Vue as well as consuming APIs. I am quite confident that I would be a valuable asset to the team.
